    "body": "@ducheng0 thanks for raising this issue! There's a lot of opportunity for more gesture based / swipe interactions. We do need to make sure gestures don't conflict. E.g. swipe in a message in a 1:1 chat can easily be misinterpreted as swipe between nav bar items (swipe to wallet) and swipe to the other user's profile.\r\n\r\nI think the issue would benefit from a global review of swipe actions and navigation. \r\n\r\ncc @pedro-et @xAlisher ",
